        "from": "backfill job",
        "to": "Step 4 deployment",
        "status": "broken",
        "issue": "No validation gate between backfill completion and read-switch deployment. An operator could trigger Step 4 while backfill is still running or after a partial failure, causing reads from an incomplete table."
